_sText: This map is designed to have a low file size, yet have a memorable experience. It's a map with 3 rooms; 2 spawn rooms and 1 main room. There are 3 routes to get from T to CT. There is a quake like jump in the middle. The screenshots really don't do this map justice, you have to play it to the get entire atmosphere. instructions for the jump in the center: - if you walk onto it you'll float across - if you jump on it you will fall down to the floor below. - if you jump from the basement you will be lifted to the floor above.
